{"type":"article","id":7931,"title":"告诫香港人，小心六四再现","uid":17086,"topics":[2143,3160],"contents":"从很多迹象表明，香港人权法案即将通过，中共要狗急跳墙了，六四即有可能在香港重现<br>\n<br>\n迹象一：<br>\n陆生紧急被叫回大陆<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JwuqomU.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JwuqomU.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JwuqomU.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n迹象二：<br>\n交通封锁<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/6eA0boO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6eA0boO.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/6eA0boO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n迹象三：<br>\n黑警在上次开枪之后，就相当克制，基本上没有发生枪案，直到今天再次发生，估计是知道是没有被制裁的后果<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/2ZNQo67.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2ZNQo67.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/2ZNQo67.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>我希望我是多疑了，杞人忧天了，但是真的不得不警惕一下中共，小心六四再现，愿天佑香港！</b>","date":"2019-11-11","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":0}